{"tid":1586011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣: 匪國篡政70年圖片","createTime":"2019-09-21T18:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:36:10.000Z","uid":62011,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca61c5cecd1a2f5eac41fa75f3442076ce791c8","tid":1586011,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:34:53.000Z","msg":"幫共匪賀佢老母建政70年<br />\n一定要搞大佢。<br />\n<br />\n何妖不是叫藍絲撕18區連儂牆？唔通你打算把舊文宣翻印了事？如果18區都湧現中共70年來的惡行，會是一個咩畫面？上到外媒報紙上，又有甚麼效果？<br />\n<br />\n只要中共分子的照片，放到兩米高，貼到牆上，一幅又一幅，人人走過這條歷史隧道，喚起了上一輩的慘痛記憶，你說對抗爭，有咩幫助？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w4ygD7u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw4ygD7u.jpg&h=e461870f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJNhoza.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJNhoza.jpg&h=7d137fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYwxWUa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYwxWUa.jpg&h=1376ce51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MD2pN0Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMD2pN0Q.jpg&h=ef3736be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Kv61kR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Kv61kR.jpg&h=7c8f989d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijQfaeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijQfaeb.jpg&h=e6393eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oCtTGkS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoCtTGkS.jpg&h=196291ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjS1Qed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjS1Qed.jpg&h=272c39ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4ntved.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4ntved.jpg&h=9fc3cd01&